description: The Chapel of the Single Shadow is the headquarters of the cult known as I.D.I.C. It is a huge black monolithic peak located in the west of the Republic of Transia at the opposite end of the country to Wundagore Mountain. The land surrounding the Chapel contain the bones of beings that archeologists say are neither animal nor human. Some are massive and local folklore states that they are the remains of gods so vast that they contained multiple souls and that they are so old they lived and died before there was a heaven.
